OL,3,CSite of street gas explosion in Derby
OL,4,Cgoes up for auction
OL,6,FEight months on from a gas explosion
OL,7,Fat a property in Derby, the explosion
OL,8,Fsite is going to be auctioned off.
OL,10,FThe site of 78 Eden Street in
OL,11,FAlvaston, which was demolished
OL,12,Ffollowing the explosion in June of
OL,13,Flast year, will go under the hammer at
OL,14,FBarnard Marcus on March 10, with a
OL,15,Fguide price of #22,000.
OL,17,FThe explosion, which was caused by the
OL,18,Fhouse's resident at the time, Paul
OL,19,FSolway, led to three properties being
OL,20,Fdemolished and a fourth home being
OL,21,Fseverely damaged.
