OL,6,FBeverley Richardson, who owns the
OL,7,Fproperty which was damaged and remains
OL,8,Fdisplaced as repair works are
OL,9,Funderway, said, "It's very positive
OL,10,Fnews.
OL,12,F"I'm glad they are doing something
OL,13,Fwith it. It makes me feel a little
OL,14,Fbetter.
OL,16,F"It's good news for everybody on the
OL,17,Fstreet, and I think it's new
OL,18,Fbeginnings after what was an awful
OL,19,Fnight on the street that nobody will
OL,20,Fever forget."
