OL,6,FSince the homes were demolished,
OL,7,Frubble has remained, and the question
OL,8,Fabout the future of the land has
OL,9,Fremained unanswered.
OL,11,FResidents have called the sight of the
OL,12,Fdemolished properties "distressing",
OL,13,Fsaying it reminded them of the
OL,14,Ftraumatic incident.
OL,16,FPaul Solway is facing prison after
OL,17,Fpleading guilty to an explosion which
OL,18,Fdestroyed the terraced house and left
OL,19,Fanother man hospitalised.
