OL,6,FEmergency services were called to
OL,7,Freports of a suspected gas explosion
OL,8,Fat around 7.24pm on June 10 last year.
OL,10,FPaul Solway, 57, admitted six counts
OL,11,Fof damaging property being reckless as
OL,12,Fto whether life was endangered,
OL,13,Frelating to six different properties
OL,14,Fat Derby Crown Court.
