OL,6,FDerbyshire Police said Solway was
OL,7,Finjured in the blast after he tampered
OL,8,Fwith the gas main at his house in Eden
OL,9,FStreet, which caused the ignition of
OL,10,Fnatural gas.
OL,12,FDetective Constable Shaun Carter said:
OL,13,F"Solway's actions on this day were not
OL,14,Fonly reckless but incredibly
OL,15,Fdangerous. It is only by pure luck
OL,16,Fthat no-one, other than Solway
OL,17,Fhimself, was injured.
