OL,6,F"Having said that, the impact this
OL,7,Fexplosion had on the residents of Eden
OL,8,FStreet and the wider community was
OL,9,Fenormous.
OL,11,F"Some people lost their homes, while
OL,12,Fothers had damage to their properties
OL,13,For vehicles. The financial cost as
OL,14,Fwell as the emotional cost and mental
OL,15,Fcost to them all cannot be
OL,16,Funderestimated.
OL,18,F"I hope that he will now spend a
OL,19,Fconsiderable period of time behind
OL,20,Fbars facing the consequences of his
OL,21,Factions."
